headline: $7,500 EV Tax Credit Extended For Tesla, Other Automakers — Kind Of
summary: The U.S. $7,500 EV tax credit expires Sept. 30, but the IRS just gave buyers a little more time to get electric vehicles from Tesla and others.

headline: Trump’s New Car-Loan Tax Break Might Break Your Brain
summary: It is about boosting all American-made autos, not just EVs, but not all buyers benefit, they must be patient and the incentive is modest.
